attributes.title: GTA V - Lindsay Wins
attributes.description: The crew sets out to let Lindsay win 1st place in an entire set of GTA V transform races. Forget about Criminal Masterminds. This is the hardest task Achievement Hunter has ever taken on.

attributes.title: GTA V - The Doomsday Scenario: Setup - Doomsday Heist (#8)
attributes.description: We attempt to purchase Agent 14 from Merryweather Security, then use the Chernobog to escort and protect Agent ULP as he escapes from his captors.

attributes.title: GTA V - The Doomsday Scenario: Setup - Doomsday Heist (#9)
attributes.description: We intercept an air convoy, take down a heavy-lift chopper, recover a Barrage ATV, then steal a Khanjali tank from a scrapyard in the desert.

attributes.title: GTA V - The Doomsday Scenario: Heist (Finale)
attributes.description: We use a Volatol jet to storm a base, clear it out, stop a warhead from launching, and save the day.

attributes.title: GTA V - Jetpack Joyrides
attributes.description: We play with the new Mammoth Thruster Jetpacks, as well as the Avengers, Deluxos, and other fun new toys in GTA V.

attributes.title: GTA V - Geoff Bag 5
attributes.description: Geoff Bag returns with four unique racing maps.

attributes.title: GTA V - Air Quota & Occupy
attributes.description: Join Michael, Geoff, Jack and Jeremy as they play new Rockstar games, Air Quota and Occupy, with Rockstar employees.

attributes.title: GTA V - Buckley Races with James Buckley and Lazarbeam
attributes.description: Two foreigners walk into the AH room. That not a joke, it's what has happened, and now they're racing in GTA V!

attributes.title: GTA V  - Geoff Bag 6
attributes.description: Geoff serves up six short racing maps, plus a bit of bonus parkour, in his sixth Geoff Bag.

attributes.title: GTA V - Stunters VS Snipers with Buckley and Lazarbeam
attributes.description: James Buckley and Lannan Eacott join us for some 8-person Snipers VS Stunters.

attributes.title: GTA V - Sprunk Your Friends
attributes.description: This stream is sponsored by the Rooster Teeth Store! Don't forget to go buy all of our awesome merch over at http://store.roosterteeth.com. The gang invites the community for a massive GTA Online session. How long can their sanity last with more than 30 cars on the road?

attributes.title: GTA V - More Stunters VS Snipers with Buckley and Lazarbeam
attributes.description: James Buckley and Lannan Eacott join us for more 8-person Snipers VS Stunters.

attributes.title: GTA V - Rear Access
attributes.description: GTA Online now lets you open the rear hatch to the Titans, so we're gonna fill that hole with our rocket bikes and supple bodies.

attributes.title: Jack Bag 3 - GTA V
attributes.description: Jack serves up five Rockstar Games Social Club maps, including stunt races, a bike race, and a stop stick/speed boost motorcycle track.

attributes.title: Charging the Wall - GTAV
attributes.description:
Achievement Hunter invites the community in for some GTA V gameplay. 30-player racing never fails to be fun. 
Join Michael, Ryan, Jack, Jeremy, Matt, and Lindsay as they race three maps with community members.

attributes.title: Community Sprunking -  GTA V
attributes.description: This stream is sponsored by the Rooster Teeth Store! Don't forget to go buy all of our awesome merch over at http://store.roosterteeth.com. Win or fail, the Achievement Hunter gang is ready for a massive race against the community. Can they prevail against more than twenty cars on the track and a firey death pit waiting to consume them?

attributes.title: Stop That Train Triple X - GTA V
attributes.description: They've tried buses, they've tried dumps, and now they're trying mobile command centers. Stop. That. Train.

attributes.title: Deadline 3: The Tron-iest We've Ever Been - GTA V
attributes.description: It's Tron gameplay in GTA V! We're back for more 'Tronny' moves and deaths in Deadline.

attributes.title: GTA V - Slippery Corner
attributes.description: Geoff showed all the guys a video where NPCs crash on a curb. Now they're all determined to get see some crashes.

attributes.title: Midair Sprunk - GTA V
attributes.description: Achievement Hunter embraces the chaos of a community transform race. It's sprunking on land, sea, and air.

attributes.title: Human Hotdog - GTA V - Deciphering Geoff
attributes.description: Geoff found some old notebooks filled with vague GTA ideas. So the guys take those ideas and make them into GTA reality.

attributes.title: It's Raining Vigilantes - GTA V
attributes.description: It took them an hour to get one rocket bike in a titan, so they decided to make it more difficult. This time they're going to get a vigilante inside that plane.

attributes.title: The Vespucci Job - GTA V
attributes.description: In this game, three cops try to stop one criminal from reaching all 15 checkpoints. Should be easy, right?

attributes.title: Hate Tunnel - GTA V
attributes.description: We're playing maps against the community! The first two are fun, and the third map is full of hate. Warning: this is one chaotic map.

attributes.title: Cruising The D - GTA V
attributes.description: We're taking every kind of plane we own (and some we don't) through the D.

attributes.title: The Greatest Mugger Who Ever Lived - GTA V
attributes.description: Trees and telephone poles are very dangerous when you go fishing for a mugger in a cargobob.

attributes.title: Death Machine Party Bus - GTA V
attributes.description: How many Achievement Hunter deaths does it take to get a party bus to the top of the mountain?

attributes.title: Big Blimpin - GTA V
attributes.description: The blimp boys are in town and ready for a fight.

attributes.title: Ragdoll Runway - GTA V
attributes.description: The game is to get to the end of the runway. But watch out! There's something very zippy zappy about those flies.

attributes.title: Blimp Country - GTA V
attributes.description: On this week's foray into GTA Online, the Blimpy Buddies are answering the most important question. "Can we put all our things on top of that blimp?"

attributes.title: Hunting Pack Remix (Part 1) - GTA V
attributes.description: One runner, two defenders, three attackers, and four maps of Hunting Pack Remix. You bet it gets brutal.

attributes.title: Geoff's Big Losses - GTA V - Hunting Pack Remix (Part 2)
attributes.description: Will Geoff be able to win a round of Hunting Pack Remix, or will he have to pay full price for the Declasse Scramjet?

attributes.title: Jack Bag 4  - GTA V
attributes.description: It's Jack bag time! Jack's picked out 5 maps featuring mario kart, wall riding, towers, cheese platforms, and Gav Slitty.

attributes.title: Salty Trap Doors - GTA V
attributes.description: Watch as salt levels rise in Rockstar's Trap Door mode.  Jack, Jeremy, and Matt face off against Geoff, Ryan, and Trevor, and the red zone becomes a state of mind just as much as the area on the map.

attributes.title: Running Back Remix - GTA V
attributes.description: We're playing new Rockstar maps in GTA V with guest twitch streamer Fiona Nova. Will Geoff be able to win a match, or will he be a loser forever?

attributes.title: Dropping Hot Death - GTA V
attributes.description: Geoff has "contemporized" his GTA V map, Jetsta La Vista, a game map where three jets will rain down war on three bicylces.

attributes.title: Jack Bag 5 With the Community - GTA V
attributes.description: The Fake AH Crew invited the community over to GTA V PC to play another selection of custom maps placed into the Jack Bag.

attributes.title: We Are Monster Truck - GTA V
attributes.description: The boys are back for Rockstar's remix of the classic adversary mode: Sumo. This time, the safe zone not only moves, but there's a time limit to get there. Things are about to get pushy.

attributes.title: Coming In Hot - GTA V with Daniel Fabelo
attributes.description:
Achievement Haunter director Daniel Fabelo joins the boys in a couple spooky rounds of Slasher II and Sumo Remix in GTA Online.
Also included in this episode: Moon Ball/Diet Coke fiascos, Achievement Haunter stories, Geoff's intestinal issues, and Gavin's dream about Michael's big you-know-what.

attributes.title: Too Fast Too Dead - GTA V w/Chilled, Ze, GaLm, & Tom
attributes.description:
We're playing Sumo Remix with the Derp Crew, and the amount of chaos that occurs is impressive. 
Chilled Chaos: https://www.youtube.com/user/CriousGamers
Galm: https://www.youtube.com/user/GaLmHD
ZeRoyalViking: https://www.youtube.com/user/ZeMachinima
Tom Fawkes: https://www.youtube.com/user/TomKitsune

attributes.title: Protecting Mr. Dooley - GTA V
attributes.description: Geoff has gathered a crew of highly trained security guards to protect  Mr. Dooley, a man with a very high bounty in a GTA V Online public server.

attributes.title: Come Out To Play - GTA V
attributes.description: Two runners try to make it to the escape spot before four boys on motorcycles kill them.

attributes.title: Sweaty Palms and Dented Wheels - GTA V: Sumo Remix
attributes.description: Ryan, Geoff, Michael, Jack, Jeremy, and Trevor are picking cars for another round of Sumo Remix.

attributes.title: Scram Jam - GTA V
attributes.description: Inspired by Jetstalavista, Ryan came up with the new game Scram Jam. This time cars will try to take down a plane.

attributes.title: KING OF THE TRAIN - GTA V
attributes.description: Geoff and his band of miscreant cowboys descend on the city of Los Santos resulting in bounties, lawmen, and the ultimate train robbery.

attributes.title: WE CAN'T ALL FIT THERE - GTA V
attributes.description: Two teams, ramps, parachutes, and increasingly difficult platforms to drop onto must mean it's time for Overtime Rumble. Watch as Ryan, Michael, and Matt take on Jeremy, Geoff, and Linsday.

attributes.title: SMASH AND KILL - GTA V: Carnage
attributes.description:
Achievement Hunter and Fiona Nova discover arena warfare with new Rockstar map, Carnage. It's pretty simple: drive, hit, boom.
Fiona Nova: https://www.youtube.com/user/fifip616
twitter.com/fionanova
